msg: o Added the method setPrefix() in the OrderedElement interface

author: elecharny
msg: Big refactoring in the Add and Delete operation :
o The Add operation is now responsible for the addition of the element at the rght place when it's an ordered table
o The Table selection can be deselected by clicking on a selected line. This allow a user to add an element at any position, as the addition is always done before the selected element, or at the end
o The delete operation reindex the prefix for ordered elements
